

I like ice  cream                   -->             Me too/ I do too./ I like ice cream too./
I don't like ice cream.             -->             Me either. / I don't either. / I don't like ice cream either.



I'm happy.                          -->             He is too./ He is Happy, too.
I'm not happy.                      -->             He is not either./ He is not happy, either.




I like ice cream.                   -->             So do I.
I don't like ice cream.             -->             Neither do I.


I'm happy.                          -->             So is she.
I'm not happy.                      -->             Neither is he.
